  "html": "<div class=\"section\" id=\"installation\">\n<h2>Installation</h2>\n<p>If you want to use Maven you can install Raven-Logback as dependency:</p>\n<div class=\"highlight-xml\"><div class=\"highlight\" style=\"background: #ffffff\"><pre style=\"line-height: 125%\"><span></span><span style=\"color: #2eb0f7\">&lt;dependency&gt;</span>\n  <span style=\"color: #2eb0f7\">&lt;groupId&gt;</span>com.getsentry.raven<span style=\"color: #2eb0f7\">&lt;/groupId&gt;</span>\n  <span style=\"color: #2eb0f7\">&lt;artifactId&gt;</span>raven-logback<span style=\"color: #2eb0f7\">&lt;/artifactId&gt;</span>\n  <span style=\"color: #2eb0f7\">&lt;version&gt;</span>7.8.1<span style=\"color: #2eb0f7\">&lt;/version&gt;</span>\n<span style=\"color: #2eb0f7\">&lt;/dependency&gt;</span>\n</pre></div>\n</div>\n<ul class=\"simple\">\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"https://docs.getsentry.com/hosted/clients/java/modules/raven/\"><em>raven dependencies</em></a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference external\" href=\"https://search.maven.org/#artifactdetails%7Cch.qos.logback%7Clogback-core%7C1.1.2%7Cjar\">logback-core-1.1.2.jar</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference external\" href=\"https://search.maven.org/#artifactdetails%7Cch.qos.logback%7Clogback-classic%7C1.1.2%7Cjar\">logback-classic-1.1.2.jar</a>\nwill act as the implementation of slf4j (instead of slf4j-jdk14).</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"usage\">\n<h2>Usage</h2>\n<p>In the <code class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">logback.xml</span></code> file set:</p>\n<div class=\"highlight-xml\"><div class=\"highlight\" style=\"background: #ffffff\"><pre style=\"line-height: 125%\"><span></span><span style=\"color: #2eb0f7\">&lt;configuration&gt;</span>\n  <span style=\"color: #2eb0f7\">&lt;appender</span> <span style=\"color: #a47ac6\">name=</span><span style=\"color: #e8535a\">&quot;Sentry&quot;</span> <span style=\"color: #a47ac6\">class=</span><span style=\"color: #e8535a\">&quot;com.getsentry.raven.logback.SentryAppender&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #2eb0f7\">&gt;</span>\n    <span style=\"color: #2eb0f7\">&lt;dsn&gt;</span>___DSN___?options<span style=\"color: #2eb0f7\">&lt;/dsn&gt;</span>\n    <span style=\"color: #2eb0f7\">&lt;tags&gt;</span>tag1:value1,tag2:value2<span style=\"color: #2eb0f7\">&lt;/tags&gt;</span>\n    <span style=\"color: #34c08b; font-style: italic\">&lt;!-- Optional, allows to select the ravenFactory --&gt;</span>\n    <span style=\"color: #34c08b; font-style: italic\">&lt;!--&lt;ravenFactory&gt;com.getsentry.raven.DefaultRavenFactory&lt;/ravenFactory&gt;--&gt;</span>\n  <span style=\"color: #2eb0f7\">&lt;/appender&gt;</span>\n  <span style=\"color: #2eb0f7\">&lt;root</span> <span style=\"color: #a47ac6\">level=</span><span style=\"color: #e8535a\">&quot;warn&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #2eb0f7\">&gt;</span>\n    <span style=\"color: #2eb0f7\">&lt;appender-ref</span> <span style=\"color: #a47ac6\">ref=</span><span style=\"color: #e8535a\">&quot;Sentry&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #2eb0f7\">/&gt;</span>\n  <span style=\"color: #2eb0f7\">&lt;/root&gt;</span>\n<span style=\"color: #2eb0f7\">&lt;/configuration&gt;</span>\n</pre></div>\n</div>\n<p>It&#8217;s possible to add extra details to events captured by the logback\nmodule thanks to the <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"http://www.slf4j.org/faq.html#fatal\">marker system</a> which will add a tag\nlogback-Marker.  The <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"http://logback.qos.ch/manual/mdc.html\">MDC system provided by logback</a> allows to add extra information\nto the event.</p>\n</div>\n", 
